item.description:
Who hasn't had this question at one time or another? You think you're doing everything you're supposed to, but nada...nothing...more lack!

It's pretty challenging sometimes to be able to observe yourself and how you're disallowing, or resisting what you're asking for. Come and bring your questions and challenges to the group, and we'll see if we can help reveal your resistance, and get you back on the vibrational track for allowing your desires to manifest.

As Abraham says, "Let's have fun with this!"

Joy, joy, joy,

Ann and Mark

P.S. PLEASE only RSVP if you know you can really attend, and give us reasonable notice if your plans change. We have been wasting handouts and food every meetup due to no-shows. Help us to be "green"! Thank you!
item.how_to_find_us: We'll be upstairs. Go to back of front lobby for stairway.
